        "text": "?type=<category> on GET /api/surfaces.json — integrators fetch one category server-side instead of pulling the full catalog + jq; unknown value 400s with the valid set, full-catalog path unchanged"
      }
    },
    "item_2": {
      "type": "Text",
      "props": {
        "text": "Filtered responses carry the category in their ETag (surfaces-v1-30-analytics) so they never collide with the full catalog in a shared cache"
      }
    },
    "item_3": {
      "type": "Text",
      "props": {
        "text": "8 new tests assert the filtered counts partition the full catalog and the no-filter call stays byte-identical"
